1553296533-IfYouWereKing.mp4_360p.mp4.title: If You Were King - by Larken Rose
1553296533-IfYouWereKing.mp4_360p.mp4.description:
Wouldn't it be great if YOU were in charge of everything? You could fix the world! Maybe. Maybe not.

"A consistent peace activist must be an anarchist." - Roderick T. Long, 'An Open Letter to the Peace Movement' http://www.peacemovement.wordpress.com

"Because the state necessarily commits aggression, the consistent libertarian, in opposing aggression, is also an anarchist." - N. Stephan Kinsella, 'What Libertarianism Is' http://mises.org/daily/3660

"Briefly, the State is that organization in society which attempts to maintain a monopoly of the use of force and violence in a given territorial area; in particular, it is the only organization in society that obtains its revenue not by voluntary contribution or payment for services rendered but by coercion." - Murray N. Rothbard, ''The Anatomy of the State' http://mises.org/pdf/anatomy.pdf

"Just as war is the natural consequence of monopoly, peace is the natural consequence of liberty." - Gustave de Molinari, "The Production of Security" http://wp.me/p2cdsV-66

1553296824-The Jones Plantation_360p.mp4.description: One cannot change reality by changing the words you use to describe reality. Look beneath the rhetoric, and glimpse the truth.
